::SnowCat::
She watched as Ramulus and Lunarpine walked closer to Spears and the 
slime bot that held her.  She turned her head to look around for 
trouble.  She looked on the bluff to her left and thought she saw a 
slight movement. She looked again and didn't see anything.  Her 
insticts told her not to dismis anything in this situation.  She 
stayed still and kept an eye out.
